.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PAYMENT-SUMMARY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-payment-summary \- summarise total payments sent and received
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-payment-summary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Aggregates completed outbound payments and paid invoices to report
total sent, total received, and net flow in millisatoshis.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{payments_sent, total_sent_msat, invoices_paid,
 total_received_msat, net_msat}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-payment-list (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-list (1)
